sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant App as AAOS App
    participant Backend as Car Pay-in Backend
    participant Redis as Redis
    participant DB as Car Pay-in DB
    participant MOLIT as MOLIT API
    participant PG as Mock PG
    participant PGDB as Mock PG DB
    participant Card as Mock Card
    participant CardDB as Mock Card DB

    User->>App: Start card registration
    App->>Backend: POST /card/order with plate, bank_name, agree_terms

    Backend->>DB: Read vehicles
    Backend->>MOLIT: Verify vehicle owner
    MOLIT-->>Backend: Return matched result

    Backend->>Redis: Save mock_pg_card_register:{order_id}
    Backend->>PG: POST /pg/internal/card-registration/sessions
    PG-->>Backend: Return public WebView URL
    Backend-->>App: Return order_id and PG WebView URL

    App->>PG: Open card registration WebView
    User->>PG: Enter card number, expiry, and CVC

    PG->>Card: Verify card
    Card->>CardDB: INSERT cards
    Card->>CardDB: INSERT card_tokens
    Card-->>PG: Return card_token and last_four

    PG->>PGDB: INSERT billing_keys
    PG->>PG: Sign raw body with PG_WEBHOOK_SECRET
    PG-->>Backend: POST /card/webhook with X-Webhook headers

    Backend->>Backend: Verify raw body HMAC and timestamp
    Backend->>Redis: Read mock_pg_card_register:{order_id}
    Backend->>DB: UPSERT vehicle_billing_keys
    Backend->>Redis: Delete mock_pg_card_register:{order_id}
    Backend-->>PG: Return webhook ok
    PG-->>App: Card registration complete
